node.text:
Adding vines creates such a peaceful vibe 😌🍃 Should we do a back to school giveaway this Monday? ❤️

Constantly seeing and being around plants helps people feel more calm and relaxed, thus decreasing levels of anxiety, while Increasing attentiveness and memory. Being around plants, whether at home or work, helps improve memory and attention span by 20 percent and can increase concentration. 🍃 #MentalHealthAwareness

node.text: Purple anyone? 💜 The color purple both calms and stimulates our minds, putting us in the right place for a focused insight 😌 It fosters creativity by awakening our senses while promoting the quiet necessary to make intuitive, insightful observations. Purple creates a harmonious balance of awareness and peace. 🙏💜 #MentalHealthAwareness
